{"tid":2454781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"昨晚鯉魚門黑幫曬馬 一被捕南亞男送院後初步陽性 觀塘警署大消毒","createTime":"2021-03-20T13:16:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T11:36:37.000Z","uid":30040,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1b36b6fd52c9aa8f00150cf9269112069d1cf741","tid":2454781,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:16:29.000Z","msg":"昨（19日）晚8時許，鯉魚門三家村牌坊一帶大批黑漢集結，疑吹雞曬馬醞釀廝殺，警方接報派遣大批軍裝警，到場鎮壓並拘捕17人。其中一名被捕南亞男子，在場表示不適送院，該男抵達醫院接受檢測後，對武漢肺炎呈初步陽性。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210320/FXY6637LKJHRLIWSN7YIAOHL2Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210320%2FFXY6637LKJHRLIWSN7YIAOHL2Y%2F&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDEYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=004804bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210320%2FFXY6637LKJHRLIWSN7YIAOHL2Y%2F&h=bf12cd25\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210320/FXY6637LKJHRLIWSN7YIAOHL2Y/</a>"},{"pid":"b3901d568460e24b30da2893a97ab0bdb5cf5c20","tid":2454781,"uid":47462,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:21:04.000Z","msg":"最緊要人有事"},{"pid":"3c0ec0d4acd6817078876aa09a0ab61acf6847c6","tid":2454781,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:21:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1feaeec732e2101444178dda0b4649dcd0b190f","tid":2454781,"uid":54800,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T11:36:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wSKBXe3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwSKBXe3.gif&h=7f2e92b3&s={SIZE}\" />3萬THX <img src=\"/assets